x4freetext: Isotopically enriched 52Cr target with thickness of
20-40 mug/cm2 evaporated onto 20 mug/cm2 carbon backing
Enge split-pole spectrograph. Delay line
counter (probably MWPC) in the focal plane was used for
position and energy loss determination
Scintillation detector placed behind delay
line counter was used for particle time-of-flight
measurement
